Source: ulog
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Abu <abu@matterize.io>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/matterizelabs/ulog
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: ulog
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, socat, moreutils, adduser
Description: USB serial port logger with automatic session management
 Logs serial data from USB devices with syslog-style timestamps.
 Features automatic daily log rotation, new log file on service restart,
 auto-start on device hotplug, and config changes are auto-applied.
 .
 Security hardened with input validation, dedicated service user,
 and systemd sandboxing.
